ode for very long unless its no drop. He loots a FS staff and a Dust of Revivacense. I say , ' can i see in trade window ? ' ..of course as my predictions suggest, he replies, 'ND.' So I say thanks for looting then, and disband. <br><br>Ya know, I have no idea what its for -the dust. I can only imagine. I would have liked to found out before he looted, and had an opportunity to roll on it if it mattered. He never gave that opportunity to any of the group. Hes a class 'A' ninja looter. After I announced to the zone his actions to alert the prospective victims, he gloated. 'thanks for killing him for me binoche'...I also recieved many tells from people in the zone regarding his history. It wasnt a good one; people were not praising him.<br><br>If I dont see some action via the guild leadership here, I will post to the Lanys Shit List...this could be taken as a threat but its not. If he will not acknowledge his actions, I will let the community have their say about him. Whether its good or bad.<br><br>I can tell you , I had a hard time NOT posting to the SL without posting here. But I have preached too much about the SL and how its used inappropriatley.<br><br>Thank you for your time in reading this.<br>Feel free to contact me via email or ingame. <br><br>____________________________________________________________<br><br>I have since found out what the nature of the loot in question. I definitely would avoid this character, he seemed very remorsless about his actions suggesting he wont hesistate to do it again.<br><br>Im sorry I had to post here..<br> <p><img src="http://home.earthlink.net/~medicnman71/_uimages/1BaseSigBinoche.jpg"></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#D5D4D5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ubolithonightshade.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bolitho Nightshade</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>w4nn4b3!</span><br> <font color=#000033>(1/29/01 4:10:54 pm)</font><br>    